---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="推免经验 · XJTUCS Guide"><section class="container simple-page"><p class="eyebrow">Recommendation experiences</p><h1 class="serif">推免经验</h1><p>这里将按届次收录投稿人自愿分享的独立经验帖。目前只提供栏目框架与投稿说明。</p><div class="empty"><strong>暂无已发布经验帖</strong><span>没有投稿的年份不会创建空目录。</span></div></section></BaseLayout>
<style>.simple-page{min-height:60vh;padding-block:80px;max-width:900px}h1{margin:8px 0 18px;font-size:5.5rem;font-weight:500;line-height:1}.simple-page>p:last-of-type{max-width:680px;color:var(--muted);font-size:1.05rem}.empty{min-height:160px;display:grid;place-content:center;gap:4px;margin-top:48px;border:1px dashed var(--line-strong);background:var(--surface);text-align:center}.empty span{color:var(--muted);font-size:.85rem}@media(max-width:680px){h1{font-size:3.4rem}}</style>
